reddit_subset.csv.description: 'RC_2008-01.ndjson' from the Arctic Shift reddit dump converted to CSV format. Meant to represent real-world data processing, and contains a very diverse range of long, complex text.

mixed_unicode.csv.description: 'item_flavor_text.csv' from the Veekun/pokedex GitHub repo. Contains medium-length text in many different languages & scripts, with many newlines.

65K_Records_Data.csv.description: Example CSV dataset used by MarkPflug/Benchmarks to benchmark .NET CSV libraries. Contains sample financial record data.

synthetic_thin_numeric.csv.description: An artificially generated dataset consisting of 4 columns containing integers ranging from 0 - 2000.

synthetic_short_numeric.csv.description: An artificially generated dataset consisting of 4 columns containing integers ranging from 0 - 2000. Short to show overall library overhead.

synthetic_quoted_numeric.csv.description: An artificially generated dataset consisting of 4 columns containing integers ranging from 0 - 2000, with each column wrapped in quotation marks for escaping.

synthetic_complex.csv.description: An artificially generated dataset consisting of 1 column with a number, and 3 containing very large escaped text designed to be extremely challenging for a parser to scan through.
